\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]And Noah was six hundred years old when the flood of waters was upon the earth.
\*[SUP]7\*[SUPX]And Noah went in, and his sons, and his wife, and his sons' wives with him, into the ark, because of the waters of the flood.
\*[SUP]8\*[SUPX]Of clean beasts, and of beasts that are not clean, and of fowls, and of every thing that creepeth upon the earth,
