\*[SUP]8\*[SUPX]And said, If Esau come to the one company, and smite it, then the other company which is left shall escape.
\*[SUP]9\*[SUPX]And Jacob said, O God of my father Abraham, and God of my father Isaac, the Lord which saidst unto me, Return unto thy country, and to thy kindred, and I will deal well with thee:
