\*[SUP]10\*[SUPX]And the taskmasters of the people went out, and their officers, and they spake to the people, saying, Thus saith Pharaoh, I will not give you straw.
\*[SUP]11\*[SUPX]Go ye, get you straw where ye can find it: yet not ought of your work shall be diminished.
