\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]And two golden rings shalt thou make to it under the crown of it, by the two corners thereof, upon the two sides of it shalt thou make it; and they shall be for places for the staves to bear it withal.
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]And thou shalt make the staves of shittim wood, and overlay them with gold.
\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]And thou shalt put it before the vail that is by the ark of the testimony, before the mercy seat that is over the testimony, where I will meet with thee.
\*[SUP]7\*[SUPX]And Aaron shall burn thereon sweet incense every morning: when he dresseth the lamps, he shall burn incense upon it.
