\*[SUP]13\*[SUPX]Remember Abraham, Isaac, and Israel, thy servants, to whom thou swarest by thine own self, and saidst unto them, I will multiply your seed as the stars of heaven, and all this land that I have spoken of will I give unto your seed, and they shall inherit it for ever.
\*[SUP]14\*[SUPX]And the Lord repented of the evil which he thought to do unto his people.
