nd the Lord spake unto Moses and unto Aaron, saying,
\*[SUP]2\*[SUPX]Every man of the children of Israel shall pitch by his own standard, with the ensign of their father's house: far off about the tabernacle of the congregation shall they pitch.
\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]And on the east side toward the rising of the sun shall they of the standard of the camp of Judah pitch throughout their armies: and Nahshon the son of Amminadab shall be captain of the children of Judah.
