\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]And his host, and those that were numbered thereof, were fifty and four thousand and four hundred.
\*[SUP]7\*[SUPX]Then the tribe of Zebulun: and Eliab the son of Helon shall be captain of the children of Zebulun.
\*[SUP]8\*[SUPX]And his host, and those that were numbered thereof, were fifty and seven thousand and four hundred.
