\*[SUP]27\*[SUPX]And the anger of the Lord was kindled against this land, to bring upon it all the curses that are written in this book:
\*[SUP]28\*[SUPX]And the Lord rooted them out of their land in anger, and in wrath, and in great indignation, and cast them into another land, as it is this day.
