\*[SUP]25\*[SUPX]For great is the Lord , and greatly to be praised: he also is to be feared above all gods.
\*[SUP]26\*[SUPX]For all the gods of the people are idols: but the Lord made the heavens.
\*[SUP]27\*[SUPX]Glory and honour are in his presence; strength and gladness are in his place.
