\*[SUP]32\*[SUPX]Let the sea roar, and the fulness thereof: let the fields rejoice, and all that is therein.
\*[SUP]33\*[SUPX]Then shall the trees of the wood sing out at the presence of the Lord , because he cometh to judge the earth.
