\*[SUP]37\*[SUPX]Yea, they sacrificed their sons and their daughters unto devils,
\*[SUP]38\*[SUPX]And shed innocent blood, even the blood of their sons and of their daughters, whom they sacrificed unto the idols of Canaan: and the land was polluted with blood.
