\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]Behold, he that keepeth Israel shall neither slumber nor sleep.
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]The Lord is thy keeper: the Lord is thy shade upon thy right hand.
\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]The sun shall not smite thee by day, nor the moon by night.
\*[SUP]7\*[SUPX]The Lord shall preserve thee from all evil: he shall preserve thy soul.
\*[SUP]8\*[SUPX]The Lord shall preserve thy going out and thy coming in from this time forth, and even for evermore.
