\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]Whither the tribes go up, the tribes of the Lord , unto the testimony of Israel, to give thanks unto the name of the Lord .
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]For there are set thrones of judgment, the thrones of the house of David.
