\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]Then they had swallowed us up quick, when their wrath was kindled against us:
\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]Then the waters had overwhelmed us, the stream had gone over our soul:
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]Then the proud waters had gone over our soul.
\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]Blessed be the Lord , who hath not given us as a prey to their teeth.
\*[SUP]7\*[SUPX]Our soul is escaped as a bird out of the snare of the fowlers: the snare is broken, and we are escaped.
\*[SUP]8\*[SUPX]Our help is in the name of the Lord , who made heaven and earth.
