\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]For the rod of the wicked shall not rest upon the lot of the righteous; lest the righteous put forth their hands unto iniquity.
\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]Do good, O Lord , unto those that be good, and to them that are upright in their hearts.
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]As for such as turn aside unto their crooked ways, the Lord shall lead them forth with the workers of iniquity: but peace shall be upon Israel.
