\*[SUP]3\*[SUPX]The Lord hath done great things for us; whereof we are glad.
\*[SUP]4\*[SUPX]Turn again our captivity, O Lord , as the streams in the south.
\*[SUP]5\*[SUPX]They that sow in tears shall reap in joy.
\*[SUP]6\*[SUPX]He that goeth forth and weepeth, bearing precious seed, shall doubtless come again with rejoicing, bringing his sheaves with him.
