\*[SUP]11\*[SUPX](She is loud and stubborn; her feet abide not in her house:
\*[SUP]12\*[SUPX]Now is she without, now in the streets, and lieth in wait at every corner.)
\*[SUP]13\*[SUPX]So she caught him, and kissed him, and with an impudent face said unto him,
